<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
</head>
<body style="background-color: #f8f9fa; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 50px auto; background-color: #fff; border-radius: 5px; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
        <div style="background-color: #dc3545; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 20px; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px;">
            <h3 style="margin: 0;">Reset Your Password</h3>
        </div>

        <!-- Image Placeholder Section -->
        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dcd6y2awx/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/PlantSeller/UI%20Images/unlock_info_plantseller" alt="Reset Password Image" style="max-width: 80%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
        </div>

        <div style="padding: 20px;">
            <p>Hello <strong><%= userName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>It looks like you requested to reset your password. Please click the button below to proceed:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <a href="<%= resetLink %>" style="padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #dc3545; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;">Reset Password</a>
            </div>
            <p>If the button above doesn't work, please click on the link below:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
                <a href="<%= resetLink %>" style="word-wrap: break-word;"><%= resetLink %></a>
            </div>

            <!-- Expiry Message Section -->
            <p style="color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold;">This link will be valid for <%= expirationTime %> minutes and will expire after that.</p>

            <p>If you didnâ€™t request this, you can ignore this email or contact support if you have questions.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The <%= companyName %> Team</p>
        </div>
        <div style="background-color: #f1f1f1; color: #666; text-align: center; padding: 10px; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px;">
            <small>&copy; 2024 <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</small>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
